      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the breed, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double-VANOS variable valve timing. The powertrain delivers linear torque across the rev range with a crisp 8,000 RPM redline, managed through a precise Getrag six-speed manual transmission and a factory M Variable Differential Lock. This specimen remains in showroom-grade condition; the chassis is structurally flawless with proactive subframe reinforcement, and the VANOS system has been overhauled to exacting tolerances. The suspension maintains its original geometry with fresh bushings and dampers, ensuring the telepathic steering response and lateral stability these cars are celebrated for. No aesthetic or mechanical deviations from the factory specification are present.",
